sts for each of the bags in the package are collected at once and as one. Hence, you can save by not having to pay for such costs per item. <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/jonathan-toews-premier-white-2015-winter-classic-2015-stanley-cup-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-19.html>http://www.um.org/hawks/jonathan-toews-premier-white-2015-winter-classic-2015-stanley-cup-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-19.html</a> <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/duncan-keith-premier-red-white-skull-2015-stanley-cup-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html>http://www.um.org/hawks/duncan-keith-premier-red-white-skull-2015-stanley-cup-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html</a> lockettor <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/chicago-blackhawks-duncan-keith-jersey.html>Duncan Keith Jersey</a>  <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/youth-duncan-keith-premier-white-away-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html>http://www.um.org/hawks/youth-duncan-keith-premier-white-away-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html</a> <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/duncan-keith-premier-black-red-skull-2014-stadium-series-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html>http://www.um.org/hawks/duncan-keith-premier-black-red-skull-2014-stadium-series-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-2.html</a> <a href=http://www.um.org/hawks/patrick-sharp-premier-black-red-skull-2014-stadium-series-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-10.html>http://www.um.org/hawks/patrick-sharp-premier-black-red-skull-2014-stadium-series-jersey-chicago-blackhawks-10.html</a>  dubleby \r\n \r\ninternet :<a href=http://www.fashionclub.dk/?canada-goose-m&aelig;nd-banff-parka-tan-p-176.html>{Canada Goose M&aelig;nd Banff Parka Tan|http://www.fashionclub.dk/?canada-goose-m&aelig;nd-banff-parka-tan-p-176.html</a>\";s:12:\"comment_type\";s:0:\"\";s:7:\"user_ip\";s:14:\"176.97.116.146\";s:10:\"user_agent\";s:127:\"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 5.1) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/40.0.2214.115 YaBrowser/15.2.2214.3645 Safari/537.36\";s:4:\"blog\";s:25:\"http://goodbyepicasso.com\";s:9:\"blog_lang\";s:5:\"en_US\";s:12:\"blog_charset\"