	(1901,833,'_feedback_email','a:4:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"[Goodbye Picasso] Contact\";s:7:\"message\";s:732:\"Name: Galen\nEmail: gsmith@kindlewood.co\nWebsite: http://kindlewood.co/\nMessage: Hey Goodbye Picasso, \r\n\r\nOur band has an opportunity to work with Sylvia Harris from Record Label Door. She has you listed on her website as one of her clients/success stories. Would you mind sharing with me what your experience has been with Sylvia? We try our best to do thorough reference checks before paying any money out to anyone and would appreciate any help you can offer. Rest assured, whatever you share would remain confidential.\r\n\r\nThank you for your time.\r\n\r\nBest, \r\nGalen\n\n\nTime: Friday August 5, 2011 at 7:18 pm\nIP Address: 173.73.127.222\nContact Form URL: http://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/\n\nSent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";s:7:\"headers\";s:109:\"From: Galen <gsmith@kindlewood.co>\r\nReply-To: gsmith@kindlewood.co\r\nContent-Type: text/plain; charset=\"UTF-8\"\";}'),
	(2225,884,'_feedback_email','a:4:{s:2:\"to\";a:1:{i:0;s:22:\"scott.c.taylor@mac.com\";}s:7:\"subject\";s:25:\"[Goodbye Picasso] Contact\";s:7:\"message\";s:578:\"Name: Steve Shay\nEmail: steveinmilford@yahoo.com\nMessage: You guys still touring/playing?  I first enjoyed you at Rockwood in NYC a few years ago, bought Book of Alyene (still on my favorite playlist on the i-pod/i-pad/i-phone), and really enjoy your skills with lyrics and music, along with your energy - talent personified!\r\n\r\nHope things are going well.  Would love to hear you sometime soon again.\r\n\r\nSteve\n\nTime: Wednesday October 30, 2013 at 10:57 am\nIP Address: 70.44.40.212\nContact Form URL: http://goodbyepicasso.com/contact/\nSent by an unverified visitor to your site.\";s:7:\"headers\";s:139:\"From: Steve Shay <wordpress@goodbyepicasso.com>\r\nReply-To: Steve Shay <steveinmilford@yahoo.com>\r\nContent-Type: text/plain; charset=\"UTF-8\"\";}'),
