	(33,1,'2010-06-24 00:11:09','2010-06-24 00:11:09','This is an example of a WordPress page, you could edit this to put information about yourself or your site so readers know where you are coming from. You can create as many pages like this one or sub-pages as you like and manage all of your content inside of WordPress.','Bio','','inherit','open','open','','2-revision-v1','','','2010-06-24 00:11:09','2010-06-24 00:11:09','',2,' http://goodbyepicasso.com/2010/06/24/2-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),
	(32,1,'2010-07-06 04:34:49','2010-07-06 04:34:49','[audio src=\"http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/07/01-Voices-Villains-Shadows-And-Ghosts.mp3\"]\r\n\r\nI\'ve got these voices in my head\r\nI swim in bottles till they\'re dead\r\n\r\nBut my ears still house their ghost when I awake\r\nAs they whisper over whit noise my mistakes\r\n\r\nBy afternoon they\'re back to life\r\nSlowly detailing my last night\r\n\r\nAnd their numbers grow with seconds I\'m alone\r\nSo I join people with voices of their own\r\n\r\nChorus:\r\nAnd the graveyards where I stay\r\nHelp to bury me each day\r\nBut I keep on hanging \'round\r\nTill my failures make no sound\r\n\r\nI\'ve got these shadows after me\r\nThey know the patterns I repeat\r\n\r\nAnd they take extensive notes on what I\'ve done\r\nThat they threaten to expose to everyone\r\n\r\nChorus\r\n\r\nDon\'t hate me\r\nI\'m a man of infinite needs\r\nAm I crazy or maybe\r\nIt\'s all just as it seems\r\n\r\nI\'ve got these villains in my soul\r\nI\'m always under their control\r\n\r\nAnd I beg and plead for every single step\r\nAs they twist and turn me like marionettes\r\n\r\nChorus','Voices, Villains, Shadows & Ghosts','','publish','open','open','','voices-villains-shadows-ghosts','','','2014-09-08 22:03:57','2014-09-09 02:03:57','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=song&#038;p=32',1,'song','',0),
