	(797,1,'2010-11-04 04:05:05','2010-11-04 04:05:05','Hot little gig in Columbus right up next to Ohio State. Ruth was a badass and brought a bunch of friends to the gig. After a BW3 intermission, we returned to the Scarlet &amp; Grey to see the headlining bands and drink $1 beers.','The Scarlet & Grey - Columbus, OH','','publish','open','closed','','the-scarlet-grey-columbus-oh','','','2014-09-08 22:08:38','2014-09-09 02:08:38','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=gallery&#038;p=797',0,'gallery','',0),
	(798,1,'2010-11-05 04:12:52','2010-11-05 04:12:52','Pittsburgh, you\'re a cool city full of colleges and sandwiches with french fries in them. This gig was more exploratory for us, checking out the vibe of the town. Thanks to Scott Satkin for providing us with an audience. We drove straight back to NYC after the gig','Shadow Lounge - Pittsburgh, PA','','publish','open','open','','shadow-lounge-pittsburgh-pa','','','2010-11-12 04:13:26','2010-11-12 04:13:26','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=gallery&p=798',0,'gallery','',0),
