	(812,1,'2010-11-13 19:43:02','2010-11-13 19:43:02','This text is completely unnecessary, but I am using it for when I try out different APIs and post an image to various services','An Image to Test With','','inherit','open','open','','scott-taylor','','','2010-11-13 19:43:02','2010-11-13 19:43:02','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2010/11/Scott-Taylor.jpeg',0,'attachment','image/jpeg',0),
	(818,1,'2011-01-18 19:35:43','2011-01-18 19:35:43','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-819\" title=\"be\" src=\"http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/01/be.jpg\" alt=\"\" width=\"500\" height=\"333\" />\r\n\r\nLads / Lasses, it\'s time to strap it on again and get ready for a kickass 2011. We are starting the year off with a show at the famed \"The Bitter End\" right in the heart of Greenwich Village and right across the street from Brian Gitman\'s 4th floor (5th floor?) walk-up.\r\n\r\nCome say hello and have a beer with us before, during, and after!','First show of 2011 @ The Bitter End on 1/21','','publish','open','open','','first-show-of-2011-the-bitter-end-on-121','','','2011-01-18 19:35:43','2011-01-18 19:35:43','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=818',0,'post','',0),
