	(833,0,'2011-08-05 19:18:10','2011-08-05 19:18:10','Hey Goodbye Picasso, \r\n\r\nOur band has an opportunity to work with Sylvia Harris from Record Label Door. She has you listed on her website as one of her clients/success stories. Would you mind sharing with me what your experience has been with Sylvia? We try our best to do thorough reference checks before paying any money out to anyone and would appreciate any help you can offer. Rest assured, whatever you share would remain confidential.\r\n\r\nThank you for your time.\r\n\r\nBest, \r\nGalen\n<!--more-->\nAUTHOR: Galen\nAUTHOR EMAIL: gsmith@kindlewood.co\nAUTHOR URL: http://kindlewood.co/\nSUBJECT: [Goodbye Picasso] Contact\nIP: 173.73.127.222\nArray\n(\n    [Name] =&gt; Galen\n    [Email] =&gt; gsmith@kindlewood.co\n    [Website] =&gt; http://kindlewood.co/\n    [Message] =&gt; Hey Goodbye Picasso, \r\n\r\nOur band has an opportunity to work with Sylvia Harris from Record Label Door. She has you listed on her website as one of her clients/success stories. Would you mind sharing with me what your experience has been with Sylvia? We try our best to do thorough reference checks before paying any money out to anyone and would appreciate any help you can offer. Rest assured, whatever you share would remain confidential.\r\n\r\nThank you for your time.\r\n\r\nBest, \r\nGalen\n)\n','Galen - 2011-08-05 19:18:10','','publish','open','open','','eb2c4781f95980ae70d38596fb0b4584','','','2011-08-05 19:18:10','2011-08-05 19:18:10','',7,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=feedback&p=833',0,'feedback','',0),
	(835,0,'2011-08-18 20:39:06','2011-08-18 20:39:06','GUITAR / BASS PLAYERS â€“ OPPORTUNITY TO TEST NEW EQUIPMENT AND GET PAID $150 FOR YOUR OPINIONS!\r\n\r\nSurvey Center focus, a market research company based in Chicago, is currently conducting a study with bands.  We are looking for people to take part in a product testing on behalf of the well known audio equipment company. \r\n\r\nYou will receive $150 for participating.  For this we would send you equipment which you would need to use during rehearsals and two shows.  After each live show we will need to you to participate in a 15 minute telephone discussion to talk about the product.  After the product testing you would be required to send the product back. \r\n\r\nTo qualify for this study you and at least one other guitar / bass player in your band must currently use a wireless system.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in participating in this study or would like more information, please to go http://bands.scfllc.com/ or contact me directly at 312-321-8150 or via email (carlys@scfllc.com). \r\n\r\nPlease be assured that this is for market research purposes only.   We are not trying to sell you anything and your details will only be used for the purposes of this study.  \r\n\r\nFeel free to pass along this information to any musicians, in working bands that you may know.\r\n\r\nBest,\r\n\r\nCarly Sullivan\r\nSurvey Center Focus, LLC.\r\nP: 312-321-8150\r\nE: carlys@scfllc.com\r\nwww.scfllc.com\n<!--more-->\nAUTHOR: carly sullivan\nAUTHOR EMAIL: carlys@scfllc.com\nAUTHOR URL: http://LookingforMusicians\nSUBJECT: [Goodbye Picasso] Contact\nIP: 173.9.251.41\nArray\n(\n    [Name] =&gt; carly sullivan\n    [Email] =&gt; carlys@scfllc.com\n    [Website] =&gt; Looking for Musicians\n    [Message] =&gt; GUITAR / BASS PLAYERS â€“ OPPORTUNITY TO TEST NEW EQUIPMENT AND GET PAID $150 FOR YOUR OPINIONS!\r\n\r\nSurvey Center focus, a market research company based in Chicago, is currently conducting a study with bands.  We are looking for people to take part in a product testing on behalf of the well known audio equipment company. \r\n\r\nYou will receive $150 for participating.  For this we would send you equipment which you would need to use during rehearsals and two shows.  After each live show we will need to you to participate in a 15 minute telephone discussion to talk about the product.  After the product testing you would be required to send the product back. \r\n\r\nTo qualify for this study you and at least one other guitar / bass player in your band must currently use a wireless system.\r\n\r\nIf you are interested in participating in this study or would like more information, please to go http://bands.scfllc.com/ or contact me directly at 312-321-8150 or via email (carlys@scfllc.com). \r\n\r\nPlease be assured that this is for market research purposes only.   We are not trying to sell you anything and your details will only be used for the purposes of this study.  \r\n\r\nFeel free to pass along this information to any musicians, in working bands that you may know.\r\n\r\nBest,\r\n\r\nCarly Sullivan\r\nSurvey Center Focus, LLC.\r\nP: 312-321-8150\r\nE: carlys@scfllc.com\r\nwww.scfllc.com \r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\n)\n','carly sullivan - 2011-08-18 20:39:06','','publish','open','open','','092b7fb430a3ff93adab2c549e5ef11f','','','2011-08-18 20:39:06','2011-08-18 20:39:06','',7,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=feedback&p=835',0,'feedback','',0),
