	(873,0,'2013-03-27 17:01:01','2013-03-27 21:01:01','Hey guys! This is Derek Dunivan from the Old Soul Revival night at the bowery electric. I was seeing if you guys wanted to play the \"big night\" we do every month. The next one is 4/24. Each artist plays 3 tunes. The theme is Willie Nelson\'s 80th bday, so we\'re trying to get every artist to play 2 originals and one Willie tune. Lemme know if you\'re interested!\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\nDerek\n<!--more-->\nAUTHOR: Derek\nAUTHOR EMAIL: ddunivan@gmail.com\nAUTHOR URL: \nSUBJECT: [Goodbye Picasso] Contact\nIP: 72.227.128.30\nArray\n(\n    [Name] =&gt; Derek\n    [Email] =&gt; ddunivan@gmail.com\n    [Website] =&gt; \n    [Message] =&gt; Hey guys! This is Derek Dunivan from the Old Soul Revival night at the bowery electric. I was seeing if you guys wanted to play the \"big night\" we do every month. The next one is 4/24. Each artist plays 3 tunes. The theme is Willie Nelson\'s 80th bday, so we\'re trying to get every artist to play 2 originals and one Willie tune. Lemme know if you\'re interested!\r\n\r\nThanks,\r\n\r\nDerek\n)\n','Derek - 2013-03-27 17:01:01','','publish','open','open','','2010b235ea7fbc2361fdd5333fabbd30','','','2013-03-27 17:01:01','2013-03-27 21:01:01','',7,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?post_type=feedback&p=873',0,'feedback','',0),
