	(2205,1,'2015-10-26 02:57:16','2015-10-26 06:57:16','https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/1679810777/goodbye-picasso-new-album-at-long-last\r\n\r\nWe\'re going back in the studio! Help us get to our funding goal! No one really \"buys\" or \"purchases\" music anymore, but we all love to listen to it. Streaming has changed the game, and most of us are listening to more music than ever. Awesome, right? This doesn\'t change the fact that recording, mixing, and packaging an album is prohibitively expensive. Help your buddies in your favorite local NYC band get their album made. It\'s been too damn long, and the music is too damn good. Love you, mean it.','Kickstarter: Goodbye Picasso - NEW ALBUM (AT LONG LAST)','','publish','open','closed','','kickstarter-goodbye-picasso-new-album-at-long-last','','','2015-10-26 02:57:16','2015-10-26 06:57:16','',0,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/?p=2205',0,'post','',0),
