	(2197,1,'2015-10-26 02:05:10','2015-10-26 06:05:10','<img class=\"alignnone size-full wp-image-855\" title=\"197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n\" src=\"http://goodbyepicasso.com/wp-content/uploads/2012/02/197658_10100933694919743_8109659_n.jpeg\" alt=\"\" width=\"720\" height=\"540\" />\r\n\r\nWe played a live set on the radio at Clemson University in July of \'11 (<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/wsbf881\" data-hovercard=\"/ajax/hovercard/page.php?id=150983448256977\">WSBF</a>). The DJ, Jordan Young, sent us the tracks. Behold:\r\n\r\n[playlist artists=\"false\" ids=\"846,847,848,849,850,851,852,853,854\"]','Live on WSBF at Clemson University','','inherit','closed','closed','','845-revision-v1','','','2015-10-26 02:05:10','2015-10-26 06:05:10','',845,'http://goodbyepicasso.com/2015/10/26/845-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),
